Rating: 4
Great base recipe. I didn't have any fresh carrots or celery, but I did have fresh sage and tomatoes from the garden. Doubled the pancetta, added a generous squeeze of a tomato/celery/carrot puree paste from a tube and threw in a piece of parmigiano reggiano rind that I had in the freezer in the last 10 minutes or so. DELICIOUS!

