Delicious, and even better on day two! Almost like a thick thick soup. My husband who is a huge pasta fagiole fan absolutely loved these. I had some fresh sage so I used it, about eight leaves sliced super thin. Worked nicely. Served with Beer Brined Grilled Pork Chops: http://www.epicurious.com/run/recipe/view?id=105298 Good dinner.

